metadata.name: Lost in Wonderland
metadata.description:
The little Lost in Wonderland has been part of our childhood for much more than being a story for children, behind it there are many stories and many secrets that make it something enigmatic to the present

This is life, sometimes it seems that we are in a wonderful world externally, with smiles, friends and success, but inside there is an earthquake of emotions and situations that alter our entire being, this painting is a reflection of those days, of those moments that actually change us and make us see what the real world is like

 Originally painted in oil and acrylic on traditional canvas
